<h1 class="text-h2 md:text-h1 text-gray-1000 mb-0px">Different Types of Stocks to Invest In: What Are They?</h1>
<div class="font-medium text-gray-800 text-md md:text-lg mb-16px mt-20px md:my-24px">
By
<a class="text-cyan-800 hover:text-cyan-600 hover:underline" href="https://www.fool.com/author/1494/">Dan Caplinger</a> 
