<section class="block-paragraph">
<p data-block-key="th8y5">Investing in the <a href="https://www.fool.com/investing/stock-market/">stock market</a> has historically been one of the most important pathways to financial success. As you dive into researching stocks, you&#x27;ll often hear them discussed with reference to different categories of stocks and different classifications. Here are the major types of stocks you should know.</p>
</section>
